                        <interp inst="t18520614-name-80" type="given" value="WILLIAM"></interp>WILLIAM WEBSTER</persName>
                  </hi> I am inspector of coin to the Royal Mint. These pieces are both counterfeit, and made of Britannia metal.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner's Defence.</hi> I was not aware it was bad; I had received some money of my employer, and had changed a sovereign; I am quite a stranger to it; I don't know bad money.</p>
